{
  "stem": "13251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had inspectors go by, and if they see any light, like it wasn't perfect, they'd knock your door and say, hey, we can see some light in that window.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Fix it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of airplanes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Airplane-- you know, because that could be seen from, from, from the air.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One thing that's real-- this house that we lived in, in Ely, can you imagine how old that house was?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was still piped for gas lighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That every room had, had-- we didn't use it because we had electricity already, but it still had the pipes in the wall for gas lighting.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every room in the house had a fireplace, every room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, well, it had to be blacked out, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- that was a very unusual building we were in, old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The exact location, I don't remember, but I was in Ely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember if I was in school, if we were at the home, but it was a happy day, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody relieved, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I didn't mention earlier, that during this whole time we were living in this home, we didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- like when we went to a movie, the cost of that movie was the most of our pocket money that we used to get.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got no other money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had an allowance-- pocket money, they called it-- a week, and it was just enough to pay for a movie, and a few pennies left.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when you say-- well, at the age of 12, I'm not going to go out and get drunk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I mean, there's-- I don't know what we did.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
